description: Magnolia Bostad AB operates as an urban development company, which develops new residential properties, including rental apartments, tenant-owned apartments, and community service properties and hotels in Sweden’s growth areas and cities. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 115 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2015-06-09. The Company’s primary activities are to acquire, own, manage, develop and sell properties. Magnolia Bostad AB develops new residential properties, including rental apartments, tenant-owned apartments, community service properties and hotels, in Sweden. The firm develops housing both for sale and for self-management.
